title: OneDrive: Access Microsoft Lists, Power BI, Loop and Whiteboard content in OneDrive for Web
description: You will be able to easily find and open your Microsoft Lists, Loops, Power BI dashboards and Whiteboard content in OneDrive for Web. If you have recently opened, shared, or favorited one of these files, then it will appear in your Recent, Shared, and Favorites views in OneDrive for Web.
